stop...

346
00:19:59,698 --> 00:20:01,427
Hang on.

347
00:20:01,466 --> 00:20:02,956
Hang on.
I can't hear you.

348
00:20:03,001 --> 00:20:04,628
Just hang on a sec.
Hang on.

349
00:20:04,670 --> 00:20:07,230
(crowd chatting)

