352
00:20:20,852 --> 00:20:22,649
Hi.

353
00:20:22,688 --> 00:20:23,677
Hey.

354
00:20:23,722 --> 00:20:25,485
- Harvey.
- Jean.

355
00:20:25,524 --> 00:20:27,583
- Harvey, good to see you.
- You too.

356
00:20:27,626 --> 00:20:29,787
- You're looking good.
- Hi.

357
00:20:29,828 --> 00:20:33,889
So our little girl's
getting married.

358
00:20:33,932 --> 00:20:36,833
(chuckles)

359
00:20:36,868 --> 00:20:40,998
Harvey, you remember the Watsons.
Barry and, of course, Jill.

360
00:20:41,039 --> 00:20:42,506
- Jill: Hi.
- Barry.

361
00:20:42,541 --> 00:20:43,599
Harvey.

362
00:20:43,642 --> 00:20:47,271
Boy, I haven't seen you guys
since Jean and I, uh...

363
00:20:47,312 --> 00:20:48,870
You look well.

364
00:20:48,914 --> 00:20:51,508
Thank you.
You look weller.

365
00:20:51,550 --> 00:20:52,812
- (both chuckle)
- Thank you.

366
00:20:52,851 --> 00:20:55,342
- Barry, you too.
- Thanks, Harvey.

367
00:20:55,387 --> 00:20:56,979
