368
00:20:57,022 --> 00:20:59,616
- Jean: Daughter.
- Jill: Betsy's fine.

369
00:20:59,658 --> 00:21:01,523
Right.

370
00:21:11,870 --> 00:21:14,668
(cellphone ringing)

