377
00:21:38,664 --> 00:21:40,564
Just have him call me, okay?

378
00:21:40,599 --> 00:21:42,829
All right.
I really got to go.

379
00:21:42,868 --> 00:21:44,301
Okay, bye.

380
00:21:44,336 --> 00:21:46,930
(crowd laughing, chatting)

381
00:21:53,145 --> 00:21:54,271
Hi.

382
00:21:54,313 --> 00:21:56,213
Kate, sorry.
I bumped into these guys.

383
00:21:56,248 --> 00:21:58,716
