Everyone, this is Kate.

384
00:21:58,750 --> 00:22:01,480
- That's okay.
- Andrew, Melissa, and Gwyn.

385
00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:02,817
- Gwen.
- Gwen, sorry.

386
00:22:02,854 --> 00:22:05,288
Sorry. I hope we're not barging in
on you.

387
00:22:05,324 --> 00:22:06,416
Kate: No, no.
Not at all. No.

388
00:22:06,458 --> 00:22:09,393
So, how do you two
know each other?

389
00:22:09,428 --> 00:22:11,157
Um, we don't, actually.

390
00:22:11,196 --> 00:22:16,293
We've got some friends in common...
Oonagh and Matt.

391
00:22:16,335 --> 00:22:20,635
And Matt came.
And Kate works with Oonagh.

392
00:22:20,672 --> 00:22:22,936
- They had to rush home.
- Bumped into each other.

393
00:22:22,974 --> 00:22:23,963
Yes.

394
00:22:24,009 --> 00:22:26,000
- Are you on a blind date?
- Yeah.

395
00:22:26,044 --> 00:22:28,911
- No. It's not a blind date.
- (all laughing)

396
00:22:30,482 --> 00:22:32,609
Shall we just leave you to it?
Shall we leave you?

397
00:22:32,651 --> 00:22:35,119
No no no no no.

398
00:22:35,153 --> 00:22:37,789
- I mean...
- (all laugh)

