407
00:23:04,549 --> 00:23:05,709
(all laugh)

408
00:23:05,751 --> 00:23:08,515
Dear Susan and dear Scott,

409
00:23:08,553 --> 00:23:09,850
I just want to take us all back

410
00:23:09,888 --> 00:23:14,951
to that wonderful holiday
