415
00:23:27,372 --> 00:23:31,240
And so, I say, many, many,
many happy, happy years ahead.

416
00:23:31,276 --> 00:23:33,710
- Salute.
- All: Salute!

417
00:23:36,281 --> 00:23:37,714
Uh, my turn.

418
00:23:37,749 --> 00:23:40,013
(cellphone vibrating)

419
00:23:41,453 --> 00:23:46,049
I thought it was off.
Sorry.

420
00:23:49,027 --> 00:23:52,519
Um...

421
00:23:55,133 --> 00:23:57,897
To a great couple.

422
00:23:57,936 --> 00:23:59,767
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

423
00:23:59,805 --> 00:24:04,105
- And cheers again!
- Cheers again.

